<div class="container">
  <div class="mb-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-light mb-2">Good evening, Vinci's parents 💕</h1>
    <p class="text-secondary">Vinci is 47 days old today</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-medium mb-4">How's Vinci doing today?</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-900/40 to-amber-800/30 border-l-4" style="border-color: var(--accent-secondary);">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3" style="background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">
            <span class="text-xl">🍼</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium">Feeding</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary">Last: 24 min ago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-3" style="background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.3);">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="text-secondary">Today:</span>
            <span class="font-medium">6 sessions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mt-1">
            <span class="text-secondary">Avg:</span>
            <span>23 min</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-900/40 to-amber-800/30 border-l-4" style="border-color: var(--accent-tertiary);">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3" style="background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">
            <span class="text-xl">😴</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium">Sleep</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary">Currently sleeping</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-3 text-center" style="background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.3);">
          <div class="text-2xl font-light mb-1">2h 34m</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-secondary">Current nap</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900/40 to-orange-800/30 border-l-4" style="border-color: var(--accent-primary);">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3" style="background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">
            <span class="text-xl">💩</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium">Diaper</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary">Last: 1h 15m ago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-3" style="background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.3);">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="text-secondary">Wet:</span>
            <span class="font-medium">5</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mt-1">
            <span class="text-secondary">Dirty:</span>
            <span>2</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="card text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3), rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2)); border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">✨</div>
      <h3 class="font-medium mb-1" style="color: var(--success);">Vinci's having a great day!</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-secondary">Vinci is getting enough sleep and feeding well. You're doing amazing! 💚</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-medium mb-4">Today's Timeline</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="timeline-item flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(68, 64, 60, 0.5);">
        <div class="timeline-icon text-2xl mr-4 w-12 text-center" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">🍼</div>
        <div class="timeline-content flex-1">
          <div class="timeline-title font-medium mb-1">Breast feeding • 25 min</div>
          <div class="timeline-meta text-sm text-secondary">
            30m ago
            <span class="ml-2" style="color: var(--success);">● Just now</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline-item flex items-center p-4">
        <div class="timeline-icon text-2xl mr-4 w-12 text-center" style="color: var(--accent-primary);">💩</div>
        <div class="timeline-content flex-1">
          <div class="timeline-title font-medium mb-1">Wet diaper</div>
          <div class="timeline-meta text-sm text-secondary">1h ago</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline-item flex items-center p-4">
        <div class="timeline-icon text-2xl mr-4 w-12 text-center" style="color: var(--accent-tertiary);">😴</div>
        <div class="timeline-content flex-1">
          <div class="timeline-title font-medium mb-1">Sleep • 85 min in crib</div>
          <div class="timeline-meta text-sm text-secondary">1.5h ago</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
